  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="KT281-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">piriviṭai vēṟuppaṭṭāḷaik kaṇṭu tōḻi vaṟpuṟuppāṭkuk kiḻatti uraittatu. </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">Spoken by HER to the one who encouraged [her], [namely]
          the confidante at the sight of her who had changed in the time of separation. </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="KT281">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l> veṇmaṇaṟ potuḷiya paiṅkāṟ karukkiṉ</l>
          <l> kommaip pōntaik kuṭumi veṇṭō</l>
          <l> ṭatta vēmpi ṉamalai vāṉpūc</l>
          <l> curiyā ruḷaittalai poliyac cūṭik</l>
          <l> kuṉṟutalai maṇanta kāṉañ</l>
          <l> ceṉṟaṉar kollō cēyiḻai namarē.</l>
        </lg>

        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
          <l>Our [man], o red-jewel[led one] , has he gone</l>
          <l rend="indent2">to the forest, where on the hills,</l>
          <l rend="indent3">worn for [their] heads with curly full mane to shine ,</l>
          <l rend="indent2">the dense sky(light) flower of the Neem tree by the path united</l>
          <l rend="indent3">with the white mass of crests of the rounded Palmyra</l>
          <l rend="indent4">with sharp edges [and] fresh stems , thriving</l>
          <l rend="indent8">in the white sands ?</l>


        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
